tip.text: The wifi password here is still cajun456.  The service here is quite bad. I finish my dish before my family got theirs. Fish came out after my brother finished a pizza and my dad finished his ribs. =(
The green tea on its own is really good. It comes with a small cup and small pot and they will refill for you whenever you want. Best to have it at the bar. Wifi password is 77320858
The flat white here is very smooth and easy to swallow. Doesn't have any acidic kick or bitter after taste which I don't like. Wifi password is wifipassword (can be found at the cashier)
This place has a very nice ambience here to chill. The staff are very friendly. Wifi password is 77313566. It's their phone number and can be found on your receipt =)
Very nice place to relax and de-stress when there are dogs roaming around and visiting you.  Wifi password is "nachocola22".  Can be found at the cashier when ordering.

The lunch deal here is very worth it.  Give it a try. The wifi password is portobellopj1.
